data.description: This is two tracts selling as one totaling 11.55 acres . This is a great mini farm in a great location. Top of the line modular, Norris built home. Quality built with attention to detail.  Crown molding and 3-1/2” finished baseboards throughout . The living room has beautiful tray ceiling and wood burning fireplace. All 3 bedrooms have large walk-in closets. Large master bedroom with spa like bathroom large shower and soaking tub. The best part is the one in a million view.  Enjoy every picture perfect season from the 10’ x 20’ foot deck.
